ComicInfo.Summary: Here, at the end of Gina's long journey through the omniverse, she must say farewell to all of the friends and allies she's made along the way. And she'll miss the little knight, the brassy "eternal squire", most of all! But when it's time to part with the fantastic tools and items she's been loaned, there is one she has... difficulty... giving up. After all, she helped procure the magicked root and its life support power. Yessss. Why shouldn't she keep it? It's... precious.
